message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: clawtouch-mcp
abstract: >-
  An MCP (Model Context Protocol) server that exposes ClawTouch USB HID
  hardware as agent tools, letting an LLM emit genuine physical keyboard and
  mouse input on a target machine over USB-CDC.
type: software
authors:
